{"tid":2218400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美司法部調查賓州郵寄投票 發現至少七張川普票被棄","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T11:02:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f14f771f8996b03b44c5fd167012f6444a1fc7c1","tid":2218400,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"美司法部調查賓州郵寄投票 發現至少七張川普票被棄<br />\n<br />\n【美麗日報2020年09月25日訊】美國總統大選在即，美國軍人和海外公民已開始提前投票，很多選票已經寄出。美司法部24日聲明說，賓州郵寄投票調查發現，有少量軍方選票被丟棄，在被恢復的9張選票中，有7張投給了川普總統，另2張被重新封裝，投票信息不詳。<br />\n<br />\n司法部最初聲明說，9張被恢復的選票均投給了川普總統，但隨後發現並更正，其中2張被選舉人員重新封裝，具體投票信息不詳。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.bld.news/news/p-462402.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bld.news%2Fnews%2Fp-462402.html&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=72066469\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.bld.news/news/p-462402.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff7eb76eb8aa776b1c0874ba5e3823eb9933dac7","tid":2218400,"uid":127575,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"郵寄投票應該要廢止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafb984dab94ed5a81d112ad7532e7b5c0f0b222","tid":2218400,"uid":38033,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"美軍應該好唔鐘意拜登依啲傻鳩呀伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6184b40f80119001c311451d8ea8535cf1b5d58","tid":2218400,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"= 大灣區投立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b77b9652ef5c80b91275eb6b82a888b85fa421","tid":2218400,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"點解可以早咁多投票?仲要唔等埋辯論?"},{"pid":"a1d1bad5a72c4156455b9d21f0579df945801c59","tid":2218400,"uid":168492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"q